2. Added verification coverage for missing/invalid review-schedule paths:
- [test_t4_1_cli_scaffold.sh](/Users/darkbit1001/workspace/waveplan-mcp/tests/swim/test_t4_1_cli_scaffold.sh:9)
- Added/updated cases:
  - Unset `WAVEPLAN_SCHED_REVIEW` for deterministic behavior.
  - Assert fail-fast error when neither flag nor env is set.
  - Assert fail-fast error when `--review-schedule` points to a non-readable path.
